                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18170219-127-off712 t18170219-127-cd713"></join>, one handkerchief, value 2s. 6d., the property of 
                     <persName id="t18170219-127-victim982" type="victimName">
                        John 
                        Stamford
                     <interp inst="t18170219-127-victim982" type="surname" value="Stamford"></interp>
